{"success":true,"message":"Group Events retrieved successfully","data":{"group_events":[{"id":"0197caf3-dd38-70f1-95ab-cb0bde874c5f","slug":"2025-summer-cme","title":"2025 Summer CME","type":"group_event","status":"published","description":"<h2>What to Expect:<\/h2><ul><li><strong>8 CME sessions<\/strong> relevant to primary care.<\/li><li><strong>Unstructured afternoons<\/strong> for relaxation or adventure.<\/li><li><strong>Opportunities to connect<\/strong> with family physicians from across Minnesota.<\/li><\/ul>","excerpt":false,"excerpt_description":"","additional_details":[{"name":"Location & Accommodations","value":"<p><strong>Conference Location<\/strong><\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.grandviewlodge.com\/\"><strong style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Grand View Lodge<\/strong><\/a><strong><br><\/strong>23521 Nokomis Ave<br>Nisswa, MN 56468<\/p><p><br><\/p><p><strong><br>Room Reservations<br><\/strong><br><\/p><p>The MAFP group rate deadline has passed. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.grandviewlodge.com\/stay\/main-property\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Contact Grand View Lodge<\/span><\/a> for room rates and availability or <a href=\"https:\/\/mafp.org\/event\/2025-summer-cme\/#options\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">explore other accommodations in the area<\/span><\/a>.&nbsp;<\/p><p><em>Please note that Grand View Lodge room reservations and cancellation policies are separate from the MAFP\u2019s event registrations and cancellation policies.<\/em><\/p><p><br><\/p><p><strong><br>About Grand View Lodge<br><\/strong><br><\/p><p>Grand View is located in Nisswa, part of the Brainerd Lakes Area. It has consistently been a top-rated Minnesota resort, and its main lodge is on the National Registry of Historic Places. Amenities include lake access, a new(er) pool and recreation facility, golf course, spa and more.<\/p><ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.grandviewlodge.com\/activities\/category\/summer\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Summer Activities at Grand View<\/span><\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.nisswa.com\/\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Nisswa: Things to Do<\/span><\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/explorebrainerdlakes.com\/\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Explore Brainerd Lakes<\/span><\/a><\/li><\/ul>"},{"name":"Continuing Medical Education","value":"<p><strong>Activity #109028:<\/strong> The AAFP has reviewed 2025 Summer Conference and deemed it acceptable for up to 6.00 Live AAFP Prescribed credit(s). Term of Approval is from 08\/18\/2025 to 08\/19\/2025. Physicians should claim only the credit commensurate with the extent of their participation in the activity.<\/p>"},{"name":"Partnership Opportunities","value":"<p>Connect with family physicians over two half-days of continuing medical education at one of Minnesota\u2019s top resorts. <strong>Limited to eight partners.<\/strong><\/p>"}],"featured_image":"https:\/\/mafp.seamlessams.com\/tenancy\/assets\/0197cb16-3ffb-73d0-b083-a302ddb2bf12\/01JZ5HCFZF22J79K79DEKA22G4.png","event_date_range":{"start":"2025-08-18T13:00:00.000000Z","end":"2025-08-19T17:00:00.000000Z"},"formatted_start_date":"Aug 18, 2025 8:00 AM","formatted_end_date":"Aug 19, 2025 12:00 PM","associated_events":[{"id":"0197caef-0b53-720d-ad27-66820170e3e6","title":"2025 Summer CME Day 1 (Monday)","slug":"2025-summer-cme-day-1-monday","start_date":"Aug 18, 2025 8:00 AM","end_date":"Aug 18, 2025 12:00 PM","formatted_start_date":"Aug 18, 2025 8:00 AM","formatted_end_date":"Aug 18, 2025 12:00 PM","venue":{"id":"0197caf7-42a6-70f8-80b2-c5c7273a0b22","name":"Grand View Lodge","google_map_url":"https:\/\/www.grandviewlodge.com\/","address_line_1":"23521 Nokomis Ave Grand View Lodge","address_line_2":null,"city":"Nisswa","state":"MN","country":"US"}},{"id":"0197caf0-5044-7063-bab1-05d959dcfe7e","title":"2025 Summer CME Day 2 (Tuesday)","slug":"2025-summer-cme-day-2-tuesday","start_date":"Aug 19, 2025 8:00 AM","end_date":"Aug 19, 2025 12: